coin USD\">BTC-USD</a>) significantly outperformed the <strong>S&amp;P 500</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust\">SPY</a>) and all other asset classes since its inception in 2009. Bitcoin was priced at zero when it began, and the price recently surpassed $100,000 before pulling back a bit. Bitcoin's rise</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156834628/image_2156834628.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743011-bitcoin-significantly-outperform-stock-market-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 17:00:25"}, {"id": "4743008", "title": "MAGS: Back To Its Best", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rolling the dice\" data-id=\"1422219755\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1014px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Roundhill Magnificent Seven ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MAGS\" title=\"Roundhill Magnificent Seven ETF\">MAGS</a></span>) had a slow start to H2, but is now back to its former ways, leading the market and outperforming. This article looks at the reasons behind the rally and why it could continue.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743008-mags-back-to-its-best", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:52:35"}, {"id": "4743007", "title": "ClearPoint: Fundamentals Continue To Improve", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Digital Brain With Connections\" data-id=\"2107031844\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">imaginima</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>While ClearPoint's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CLPT\" title=\"ClearPoint Neuro, Inc.\">CLPT</a></span>) share price has stagnated in recent months, even as the broader market has surged higher, there have been a number of positive developments. In particular, ClearPoint's laser therapy and drug delivery businesses appear set to continue driving strong</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743007-clearpoint-fundamentals-continue-to-improve", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:50:34"}, {"id": "4743020", "title": "VersaBank 2024 Q4 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by VersaBank in conjunction with their 2024 Q4 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106079\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743020-versabank-2024-q4-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:36:14"}, {"id": "4742943", "title": "Retail Sector Earnings Roundup: Analyzing The Holiday Season Winners And Losers", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Shop owner handing bag to smiling client after shopping in clothing boutique\" data-id=\"1217476252\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The holiday shopping season is in full swing, and a broad range of retailers have reported results, with many surpassing sales and earnings expectations. The macroeconomic environment continues to favor retailers with a strong value-driven product mix, benefiting giants like Walmart (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742943-retail-sector-earnings-roundup-analyzing-the-holiday-season-winners-and-losers", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:30:00"}, {"id": "4742835", "title": "1 REIT To Sell And 1 Strong Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sold sign in front yard of house\" data-id=\"109350551\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Martin Barraud</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>REITs (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VNQ\" title=\"Vanguard Real Estate ETF\">VNQ</a>) have strongly recovered over the past year, earning investors a 40% return in a single year:</p> <p></p> <p>However, this recovery was very uneven across the REIT sector.</p> <p>Some surged by 100%+ while others were left stagnating behind, and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742835-1-reit-to-sell-1-strong-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:25:00"}, {"id": "4743002", "title": "Datadog Poised To Rule 2025's AI Software Picks", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/517395625/photo/dog-running-for-frisbee-in-field.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=EYa8eRM7IRx4bwyb6qjHWC5Jl08BwnRP-um6h1bsnLg=\" alt=\"Dog running for frisbee in field.\" data-id=\"517395625\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dougal Waters/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Through most of 2024 I have stayed neutral on data observability company Datadog (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DDOG\" title=\"Datadog, Inc.\">DDOG</a></span>) as the broader software space that it operated in fell out of the prioritization order among enterprise</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743002-datadog-poised-to-rule-2025s-ai-software-picks", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:16:13"}, {"id": "4743012", "title": "How The U.S.-China Trade Dispute Is Redefining Global Trade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"American Chinese windy day flags fly together on flagpole\" data-id=\"515912196\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5760px\" height=\"3840px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">cbarnesphotography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/inga-fechner/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Inga Fechner</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/james-knightley/\" rel=\"nofollow\">James Knightley </a></em></p> <h2>China\u2019s declining US market share</h2> <p>The global market landscape has undergone significant transformations since the onset of the US-China trade dispute in 2018. The imposition of tariffs and a shift towards protectionism have</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743012-how-us-china-trade-dispute-redefining-global-trade", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:09:00"}, {"id": "4741580", "title": "Allied Gold: Where Growth And Value Intersect", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"native 1.05 gram gold nugget from Kenieba District, Mali, Africa\" data-id=\"1638258887\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Bjoern Wylezich</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>All figures are in United States Dollars unless otherwise noted. G/T = grams per tonne (of gold or silver). GEOs = gold-equivalent ounces. SEOs = silver-equivalent ounces. AISC refers to all-in sustaining costs. LOMP = life of mine plan.</p> <h2>Introduction</h2>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741580-allied-gold-where-growth-and-value-intersect", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:05:00"}]}